00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Turning a corner the music we had been hearing became louder and at last we saw the musicians themselves.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:15,000
They were so involved they failed to hear us. The music was suited to the scene - a moody, romantic melody.

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:22,000
We stopped to listen and I admit that I, too, was affected by the sound as well as by the spectacle of the masked players.


5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:29,000
One of the visitors noticed me listening. "Beautiful music, don't you think?"


